msgid ""
"**TYPE_VALUE** = **0** --- Value tracks set values in node properties, "
"but only those which can be Interpolated."
msgstr "**TYPE_VALUE** = **0** —— 值轨道在节点属性中设置值，但仅是可以被插值的属性。"

